{"tid":1630370,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港臨時議會運作團隊 : 特別鳴謝工聯會陸頌雄提供行動綱領。","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:55:26.000Z","uid":30274,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d60372ec2030e688f65d6a6869c07ce978d2da80","tid":1630370,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"自己睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongparliament/photos/a.103888391019258/103888157685948?type=3&amp;sfns=mo&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongparliament%2Fphotos%2Fa.103888391019258%2F103888157685948%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo%26__tn__%3D-UK-R&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=b9717e29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongparliament/photos/a.103888391019258/103888157685948?type=3&amp;sfns=mo&amp;__tn__=-UK-R</a><br />\n<br />\n兒登仔唔想比人再話係兒登仔, 唔該用下腦<br />\n而家搞港獨=比藉口共產黨出兵平亂=<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要收香港人既皮</span></span><br />\n呢班香港臨時議會係咩人, 用下腦都知佢想點<br />\n唔怕講埋開口牌, 而家一定係先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雙普選, 再行自治</span></span>, 之後先有基礎有國際認受性決定最後獨立與否<br />\n你老味而家叫獨立, 獨立最緊要係乜? 一就係自身武力, 你有槍有炮有軍隊?? 冇既就得另一條路, 要國際社會, 當然<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尤其係美國承認</span></span>, 共產黨要郁你唔係咁易(類似既參考台灣現況)<br />\n而家乜春都冇就大叫獨立, 外界得到訊息係支那有內亂, 所以佢派軍隊鎮壓係合理, 咁大家得死啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個香港臨時議會係咩人, 大家心知肚明啦<br />\n支那派出既卧底組織, 唔好中呢D低級招數OK?<br />\n<br />\n美人警告《香港臨時政府宣言》或遭官方滲透 疑為軍隊鎮壓提供借口<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191006-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%A3%E8%A8%80%E6%88%96%E9%81%AD%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F-%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%80%9F%E5%8F%A3?fbclid=IwAR3bQfEqfojBjBPR5_Xn0BdzOIndAln8-Jdtj1OAyCKPPIadbxoBMUJeBps&amp;ref=fb_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihk