l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ea9ff05917c51295bb02d04aad404b4d1b8c55","tid":1630370,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟！一齊拆！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：共產黨玩嘢，香港人領嘢。咁都領嘢？枉為香港人。香港人不聽陳雲的話，犯上政治錯誤，犧牲幾多人都是被共產黨收割，之後糟蹋。<br />\n如果你識字，就知道第一句是共產黨的意識形態。破舊立新，而且強調歷史發展的必然性。<br />\n香港人昨晚十八區，宣讀共產主義宣言，而且宣言隻字不提美國為香港人權立法監護香港的貢獻，美國的有識之士被香港人激死了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157462752772225%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=aa371291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時有香港獨立黨出聲明攻擊香港人權及民主法、又有臨時議會成立、又有臨時政府成立、又有連登「我有個讀政治的朋友」寫了香港憲法？同時又有練乙燈出文再提港獨？全部舉動幾日內急急推出，全部都是指向推翻美國「人權及民主法」的保障香港自治的立法前設？全部都是港共用了緊急法之後才忽然出現？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002094159071%2Fposts%2F2498430470236734%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=4536babe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"83e7c0bc09d21633c2a3b8f6b10aa124cc2e64cf","tid":1630370,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8cbff78e4c1aca9f6b2290b2ae7cad9b50d574","tid":1630370,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:02:58.000Z","msg"